{"id":548030,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/01/人民网-数读舆情：小粉红群体是如何崛起的/","date":"2017-01-02T02:48:48Z","modified":"2017-01-02T02:48:48Z","title":"人民网 | 数读舆情：“小粉红”群体是如何崛起的？","content":"<p>2016年网络舆论场中一个引人瞩目的现象是“小粉红”群体的崛起，表现出强烈的爱国热情和对体制的捍卫。在微博平台中，数量庞大的“小粉红”凝聚在一批共青团系统官方微博周围，在“帝吧出征”反“台独”、表情包大战、电影《没有别的爱》争议、南海仲裁案等涉及爱国表达的热点事件中，表现出90后强大的自我动员与组织能力。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/MAIN201612301549000319052155134.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-548031\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/MAIN201612301549000319052155134.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1230\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/MAIN201612301549000319052155134.png 500w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/MAIN201612301549000319052155134-122x300.png 122w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/MAIN201612301549000319052155134-416x1024.png 416w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/MAIN201612301549000552849598082.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-548032\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/MAIN201612301549000552849598082.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1529\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/MAIN201612301549000552849598082.png 500w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/MAIN201612301549000552849598082-98x300.png 98w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/MAIN201612301549000552849598082-335x1024.png 335w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20505],"tags":[8635,8931,16016,30038,9465,9369,25859,30040]}